<HEAD>Aquino Staffer Dies as President Weeps</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MANILA, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Corazon Aquino's chief
housekeeper died of cancer today with a weeping president at her
bedside, the presidential palace announced.
   Mrs. Aquino stayed by Priscilla Ruiz Aragon's side for two hours
until she died at the suburban Makati Medical Center, according to
